Title: Statistics of the Composite System
Authors: Hitoshi Ito
Comments: 4pages
\\
  The space-like asymptotic limit of the bilocal composite field of the state
consisting of a nucleus and an electron is studied. It is shown that the
resulting local field of an atom satisfies the proper commutation relations in
the sub-Fock-space of the atom.
